data.description: Priced to sell - Motivated Seller - 1.59 acres in the desirable NE area of Golden Gate Estates. Meets County requirements for a GUEST HOUSE! ; this beautiful newly built in 2021- 3 bedroom, 2 bath and 2 car garage is move in ready. House has bright open floorplan with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, upgraded refrigerator and newer washer and dryer.  Tray ceiling, walk-in closet in primary bedroom. Tile throughout, crown molding, impact windows, automatic irrigation and asphalt driveway. Very well located with immediate access to Everglades and Immokalee Rd, Publix, CVS, and Big Corkscrew Island Regional Park just to mention a few conveniences! Bring trucks! NO HOA fees! Ready set GO!
